| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: c DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |   Projection: hits.SearchPhrase, count(Int64(1)) AS c                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.SearchPhrase]], aggr=[[count(Int64(1))]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |       Filter: hits.SearchPhrase != LargeUtf8("")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |         TableScan: hits projection=[SearchPhrase], partial_filters=[hits.SearchPhrase != LargeUtf8("")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [c@1 DESC], fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[c@1 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[SearchPhrase@0 as SearchPhrase, count(Int64(1))@1 as c]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |       AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[SearchPhrase@0 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[count(Int64(1))]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |         CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([SearchPhrase@0], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[SearchPhrase@0 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[count(Int64(1))]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |               SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                   DataSourceExec: file_groups={16 groups: [[/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], [/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], [/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], [/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], [/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>, /data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], ...]}, projection=[SearchPhrase], file_type=vortex, predicate: SearchPhrase@0 !=  |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
